    <p>Please make sure to follow our <strong>Standard Operating Procedures</strong> and airline rules at all times. You are kindly requested to fly only your assigned aircraft using the provided registrations.</p>

    <p class="section-title">üåê Start Flying!</p>
    <p>Join us on Newsky: <br>
      <a href="https://newsky.app/airline/CMT/info" target="_blank">https://newsky.app/airline/CMT/info</a></p>

    <p>Before your first flight, we recommend:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>üìò Reading our SOP (<a href="#">link</a>)</li>
      <li>‚úàÔ∏è Downloading liveries from the <a href="https://comet-jet-site.vercel.app/livery.html">LIVERIES</a> section (password: <code>ComJetPlenCP24</code>)</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="section-title">üîê Pilot Portal Login</p>
    <p><strong>Login Email:</strong> <%= email %><br>
      <strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= tempPassword %><br>
      <em>This is a one-time password. Please change it after your first login.</em>
    </p>

    <div class="signature">
      <p>We're thrilled to have you flying with us.<br>
        If you need help, don't hesitate to reach out via <strong>Discord</strong> or email.</p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 20px;">
        Blue skies,<br>
        <strong>KayJayKay & Aviaced</strong><br>
        CEOs ‚Äì CometJet VA
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Twinkling stars
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const body = document.querySelector('body');
      for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
        const star = document.createElement('div');
        star.classList.add('twinkling-star');
        star.style.width = `${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px`;
        star.style.height = star.style.width;
        star.style.left = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
        star.style.top = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
        star.style.animationDelay = `${Math.random() * 5}s`;
        body.appendChild(star);
      }

      // Confetti effect on load
      const card = document.querySelector('.card');
      for (let i = 0; i < 30; i++) {
        const confetti = document.createElement('div');
        confetti.classList.add('confetti');
        confetti.style.left = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
        confetti.style.top = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
        confetti.style.backgroundColor = `hsl(${Math.random() * 60 + 180}, 100%, 70%)`;
        confetti.style.transform = `rotate(${Math.random() * 360}deg)`;
        confetti.style.width = `${Math.random() * 8 + 4}px`;
        confetti.style.height = `${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px`;
        confetti.style.animation = `fadeInUp ${Math.random() * 0.5 + 0.5}s ease-out ${Math.random() * 0.5}s forwards`;
        card.appendChild(confetti);
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>

</html>
